narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this student to someone who wants the freedom to explore topics of his interests. The course readings focused mostly on Chinese medicine, but the research project was a little more flexible.
Take this class if you are interested in Chinese technology and science. Very cool stuff
